+# PR 214 Remediation Report
+
+## Thread Classification
+
+All visible threads from `.github/review_export/pr_214_threads.json` were classified before editing code.
+
+- `T-214-01`: actionable
+- `T-214-02`: duplicate of `T-214-01`
+- `T-214-03`: obsolete outdated hunk
+- `T-214-04`: actionable
+- `T-214-05`: actionable
+
+## Code and Doc Remediation
+
+- `src/policy/approval_router.py`: normalized `approval_state` inside `build_policy_preview(...)` before calling `build_preview_payload(...)`.
+- `src/policy/preview.py`: fallback payload now includes `approval_state` and `requires_human_review` in addition to `status`.
+- `tests/test_preview.py`: added fallback regression coverage for `preview_enabled=False` plus `manual_review` normalization.
+- `docs/approval_policy.md`: updated the fallback example and notes to match the corrected payload.
+
+## Verified Behavior
+
+The corrected fallback call shape is now:
+
+```python
+build_policy_preview(
+    request_id="req-214",
+    approval_state="manual_review",
+    preview_enabled=False,
+    actor="review-bot",
+)
+```
+
+Expected fields after normalization and fallback routing:
+
+```json
+{
+  "request_id": "req-214",
+  "status": "preview_unavailable",
+  "actor": "review-bot",
+  "approval_state": "human_review_required",
+  "requires_human_review": true
+}
+```
+
+## Validation
+
+Ran:
+
+```bash
+python -m pytest tests/test_preview.py tests/test_approval_router.py
+```
+
+Result: `5 passed`
